spans.text: To probe the bosom top severely tried
sighs to speak thy melancholy name
thy spirit wail in every storm
the sword with more than woman's hand
damp the purpose of my soul
Save Rapture's homage to your conscious charms
all its tender strings with anguish torn , And bleeds at perjured Pride's inhuman scorn
thy dark foreboding brow , What time thy bosom scorned its dearest vow
does my soul this gush of anguish feel
my soul this gush of anguish feel
Cold on my heart the hand of terror lies ; And shades of horror
'twas a deed of Murder's deepest grain
B—k's soul so true to wrath remain
thy sheeted spectre stand , Roll the dim eye , and wave the paly hand
this fluttering spark of vital flame
Welcome the dreamless night of long repose
